Package com.phunware.mapping

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PwMapViewLayer
    This is a layer that should be drawn on the map view.
    PwOnBuildingDataListener
    Used as a callback for when map data has been loaded.
    PwOnMapLoadCompleteListener
    Called when the map has data and at least the first image to display.
    PwOnMapViewStateChangedListener
    Callbacks for when the PwMapView's state changes.
    PwOnPOIClickListener
    Used to get a callback when a POI (Point of Interest) has been clicked.
    PwOnPOIDataListener
    Callback for getting point of interests for a building.
    PwRouteCallback
    Callback for getting route data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PwMappingModule
    Get an instance of the PwMappingModule to install into the Core session.
    PwMappingUtils
    Convenience methods to help with common operations on building and point data.
    PwMapView
    Designed to display vector based images, or a set of multiple LOD (level of detail) vector images.
    PwMarkerLayer
    Add markers on this layer
    PwRouteLayer
    This is a layer for a PwMapView that displays a route on the map.
